111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634226927\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe badges!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(The acheivements)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, this stuff?\u00A0\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://invisioncommunity.com/profile/49-charles/badges/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://invisioncommunity.com/profile/49-charles/badges/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022n4v1kkG.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022384.88\u0022 height=\u00221120\u0022 width=\u0022291\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/n4v1kkG.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat would be the benefit of adding that, in your view?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-14T17:28:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224042978\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634230378\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209133\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceman.Spiff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Spaceman.Spiff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEh, the forum doesn\u0027t need any random extra stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s been the general feeling from most of the forum about updates so far. The userbase doesn\u0027t seem to want large changes, and in general I feel that our community is a good enough reason to stick around without having a badge for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kapitalizing Every Word","CreatedById":212780,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T11:15:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Can you ask for a temporal ban? I had a friend who had to study for a group of exams some years ago and because he didn\u0027t want to lose concentration he asked the mods of another forum for a 1 week ban until the studies where over .\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI don\u0027t know if they gave him the ban but he passed the exams\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T11:18:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043202\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634296510\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212780\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kapitalizing Every Word\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Kapitalizing Every Word said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0Can you ask for a temporal ban? I had a friend who had to study for a group of exams some years ago and because he didn\u0027t want to lose concentration he asked the mods of another forum for a 1 week ban until the studies where over .\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI don\u0027t know if they gave him the ban but he passed the exams\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have done that in the past for a variety of reasons.\u00A0\u00A0 If anybody feels the need to step away from the forums, and doesn\u0027t feel they have the will power to do so, drop one of us a PM, and we\u0027d be happy to work with you to find a solution that fits your needs.\u00A0 We\u0027d much rather see somebody willingly be prevented from accessing the forums for a short time, rather than let them get overwhelmed with real life issues and lose the means to ever come back.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T12:54:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634296736\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have done that in the past for a variety of reasons.\u00A0\u00A0 If anybody feels the need to step away from the forums, and doesn\u0027t feel they have the will power to do so, drop one of us a PM, and we\u0027d be happy to work with you to find a solution that fits your needs.\u00A0 We\u0027d much rather see somebody willingly be prevented from accessing the forums for a short time, rather than let them get overwhelmed with real life issues and lose the means to ever come back.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYet another reason why the KSP forums are the best social media site.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T14:09:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043226\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634302447\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYet another reason why the KSP forums are the best social media site.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn all honesty, I spend more time here than on Fartbook.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T14:10:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043245\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634306956\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn all honesty, I spend more time here than on Fartbook.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only other form of social media that I have is Discord and I only use it on the weekends now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T15:51:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043247\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634307050\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only other form of social media that I have is Discord and I only use it on the weekends now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm on Discord, too. Use it for keeping in touch with some acquaintances, family, friends, and pesky students.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T15:53:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043277\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634313097\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm on Discord, too. Use it for keeping in touch with some acquaintances, family, friends, and pesky students.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll have to send you a friend request sometime!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stormbird","CreatedById":216910,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-18T08:34:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSearched for the whole forum, but could not find an answer: is there a way to participate in KSP localization? I see some misprints, mistakes and even untranslated text in Russian translation and would like to contribute. Have an experience in translating another game in the past.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-18T09:27:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224044229\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634546078\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216910\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stormbird\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, Stormbird said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSearched for the whole forum, but could not find an answer: is there a way to participate in KSP localization? I see some misprints, mistakes and even untranslated text in Russian translation and would like to contribute. Have an experience in translating another game in the past.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi Stormbird! It\u0027s nice of you to want to help out. There was a post by one of our community managers here. It\u0027s a few years old, but he gives an email address you could try writing to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022167737\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7100501478\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/141599-translations-plans-for-the-future-3-yrs-after-my-1st-question/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=2931769\u0026amp;embedComment=2931769\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:297px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-20T22:16:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happened to the scrollable forum signatures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T00:11:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224045272\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634768168\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happened to the scrollable forum signatures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpdate killed them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T00:15:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224004983\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221626322945\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/15/2021 at 12:22 AM, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s actually an unborking- signatures were never supposed to be scrollable, but we were able to restore their previous functionality in this round of updates.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T12:51:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI miss them\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:valsob:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/val_head_sob.png\u0022 title=\u0022:valsob:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T13:37:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuestion: How does somebody like \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/200262-vabab5sunnet/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022200262\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/200262-vabab5sunnet/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@\u003Cspan class=\u0022__cf_email__\u0022 data-cfemail=\u0022087e696a696a483d7b7d6626666d7c\u0022\u003E[email\u0026#160;protected]\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0get negative reputation?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T13:52:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224045497\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634823427\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuestion: How does somebody like \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/200262-vabab5sunnet/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022200262\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/200262-vabab5sunnet/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@\u003Cspan class=\u0022__cf_email__\u0022 data-cfemail=\u002280f6e1e2e1e2c0b5f3f5eeaeeee5f4\u0022\u003E[email\u0026#160;protected]\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0get negative reputation?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a bug in the forum software at some point. On some other forums, you can also click \u0022dislike\u0022 instead of only \u0022like\u0022, and so this kind of thing would be much more common if we allowed that here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T14:01:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224045511\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634824373\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a bug in the forum software at some point. On some other forums, you can also click \u0022dislike\u0022 instead of only \u0022like\u0022, and so this kind of thing would be much more common if we allowed that here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlad to see we\u0027re a\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022j6sGDKQ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022125.00\u0022 height=\u0022120\u0022 width=\u002296\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/j6sGDKQ.png\u0022\u003E\u00A0forum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T14:43:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224045272\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634768168\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat happened to the scrollable forum signatures?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am glad they are gone for a variety of reasons, the most obvious is they add extra length to posts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSadly, we have some forum members who would want to see how long they could make their signatures. Signatures are supposed to take up a very small amount of \u0022visual real estate\u0022 essentially enough to tell the person viewing it a little more about you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/111158-ask-the-mods-questions-about-the-forums/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=4005142\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EA few posts back in this thread\u003C/a\u003E, I discuss setting up a status update and using it as a static page that you could paste the link to it in your signature. The status update can be updated can be updated just as any other forum post can be updated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-10-21T14:44:19Z\u0022 title=\u002210/21/2021 02:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 21, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by adsii1970\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded hot link to the related post\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T14:47:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224005142\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221626357899\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/15/2021 at 9:04 AM, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I agree. Long signatures can be annoying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, I have been thinking of this for a while. One of the things our forum software is missing is a fully customizable \u0022about me\u0022 page. In my mind\u0027s eye, it is where folks could share more about themselves, within the scope of the forum guidelines, but without bogging down the signature area.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne of the best ways to create a \u0022profile page\u0022 where folks can create a brag page. Here\u0027s how you could do it:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E1. Go to your profile page and activate status updates. \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SbwBLr0.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SbwBLr0.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002263.25\u0022 height=\u0022614\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SbwBLr0.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/RQzR0xR.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022RQzR0xR.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002263.25\u0022 height=\u0022597\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/RQzR0xR.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E2. Go to the status update you want to use as a static page, sorta like an extension of your profile page or Facebook \u0022about me\u0022 section. Click on the date of the status update.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wwbW9CE.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022wwbW9CE.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002263.25\u0022 height=\u0022597\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wwbW9CE.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003E3. The forum software will now open the status update as a single page with its own URL:\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5j2AOBP.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00225j2AOBP.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002263.25\u0022 height=\u0022597\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5j2AOBP.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can now use that URL in any part of the forum (for example, as a link in your signature), and any other place externally, that allows for URLS to be entered. It will always direct to the singe status update and not to your activity feed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope this helps some of you who want to have the \u0022brag page\u0022 in the signatures and just cannot confine it to the abbreviated version. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll have to do this some time!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T14:48:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224045559\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634827642\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210823\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AtomicTech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, AtomicTech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll have to do this some time!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve added the url to the \u0022how to\u0022 post in my signature to make it easier for folks to find in the future.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T15:25:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinally! I got one!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}